code: @Override public void mapPartition(Iterable<T> values, Collector<T> out) throws Exception {     RandomSampler<T> sampler.     long seedAndIndex = seed + getRuntimeContext().getIndexOfThisSubtask().     if (withReplacement) {         sampler = new PoissonSampler<>(fraction, seedAndIndex).     } else {         sampler = new BernoulliSampler<>(fraction, seedAndIndex).     }     Iterator<T> sampled = sampler.sample(values.iterator()).     while (sampled.hasNext()) {         out.collect(sampled.next()).     } }
